data.description: **PRICE REDUCTION** Presenting this beautiful home located in one of the most desirable locations in Orlando. With it's close proximity to all the attractions and main highways central FL has to offer, you'll see why Sky Lake South is one of the most highly sought after neighborhoods in Orlando. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home sits on 0.26 acres and is a private oasis with an underground pool and vinyl fenced-in backyard! It's immense green yard comes complete with tropical palm trees & beautiful blooming plants. This property is located in a cul-de-sac which means you have the comfort of having no traffic and safety for playing out front. The cul-de-sac also provides extra space between homes and adds more privacy away from neighbors. For storage there is a Smithbilt 10 x 16 shed in the backyard complete with flooring that would make a great workshop! The bonus room can accommodate a 4th bedroom. A second air conditioning unit was installed with ductwork to cool the garage if desired. Wiring for a 220v hot tub is in place in the backyard. A half bath has been put in as you enter the garage which is convenient for guests. The kitchen has been remodeled with 2 year old appliances, granite counter tops and 30" cabinets. New water resistant laminate flooring throughout, new interior paint and updated master bathroom. New pavers installed by the main entrance and is equipped with a screen enclosure for a comfortable seating area. Brand new vertical blinds added to all windows including the sliding doors! New roof installed in September 2023! Vaulted ceiling in the great room is adorned with large wooden beams which adds a touch of elegance along with a new ceiling fan & new light fixtures! The neighborhood offers 2 playgrounds, tennis court, basketball court, pavilion and a lake. Located only 2 miles from all schools. From this home, you will be 20 minutes from Disney, Universal Studios or the Orlando International Airport and only 11 minutes from Sea World! Shopping and restaurants all close by. Don't miss out, come see this beautiful home for yourself.
